WEBVTT

01:34.880 --> 01:37.720
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL OF THE SAME NAME
BY ZHU YI ON WWW.JJWXC.NET

01:45.240 --> 01:46.760
WHIRLING SAND AND FLYING STONES

01:46.840 --> 01:48.240
TAKE IN THE DISCIPLE

01:50.360 --> 01:52.080
WARM WATER: SEEKING A MENTOR TO HELP ME

01:57.200 --> 02:01.520
YOUR LEVEL ISN'T UP TO 65
YOU'RE NOT QUALIFIED TO BE A MENTOR YET

02:15.800 --> 02:17.560
LEVEL UP

02:18.440 --> 02:20.200
Hey, Mom says come out for dinner.

02:21.160 --> 02:23.680
We're celebrating the New Year.
What are you doing in your room?

02:25.240 --> 02:26.680
Mom!

02:26.760 --> 02:28.960
My brother won't even talk to me!

02:34.320 --> 02:36.680
LEVEL UP

02:37.280 --> 02:38.600
Sang Yan,

02:38.680 --> 02:41.400
your uncle and aunt are visiting us.

02:41.480 --> 02:43.080
Come out and greet them.

02:43.160 --> 02:44.240
LEVEL UP

02:44.320 --> 02:45.480
Sang Yan?

02:47.720 --> 02:49.600
LEVEL UP

02:53.320 --> 02:54.880
LEVEL UP

02:54.960 --> 02:56.480
WARM WATER: TAKE IN THE DISCIPLE

02:56.560 --> 02:57.960
APPLICATION SUCCESSFUL

03:13.040 --> 03:14.000
3,413 DAYS

03:22.760 --> 03:24.800
- How many people are in your group?
- Just me.

03:31.840 --> 03:33.240
- How many people are in your group?
- Two.

03:34.760 --> 03:35.800
Thank you.

03:36.560 --> 03:37.920
How many people are in your group?

03:38.000 --> 03:38.840
One, right?

03:38.920 --> 03:40.400
Did you bring your phone?

03:41.200 --> 03:42.400
Here, scan this.

03:46.200 --> 03:47.720
- What are you watching?
- What?

03:55.440 --> 03:57.280
You can check in now.

04:34.840 --> 04:36.160
Are you afraid of heights?

04:38.400 --> 04:40.600
There's no such thing
as fear in my dictionary.

04:50.240 --> 04:52.720
Isn't someone here afraid of ghosts?

04:57.440 --> 04:58.920
That's not the same thing.

05:24.160 --> 05:25.000
Are you bored?

05:29.200 --> 05:30.400
The view is quite beautiful.

05:37.840 --> 05:38.800
It seems we're almost at the top.

05:45.880 --> 05:48.360
- What's wrong?
- Are you scared?

05:50.920 --> 05:52.160
No.

05:52.240 --> 05:54.800
I think it's really pretty.

05:55.400 --> 05:56.400
It's very healing.

06:18.040 --> 06:21.160
- Hello?
- Yan, just a heads-up.

06:21.240 --> 06:23.320
Master Chen Junwen did a reading for me.

06:23.400 --> 06:25.600
He said the 8th day of the New Year

06:25.680 --> 06:27.160
is a day with perfect timing,
good fortune, and…

06:27.240 --> 06:28.800
- Harmony.
- And harmony.

06:28.880 --> 06:31.560
So, I'm planning to have
my wedding on the 8th.

06:31.640 --> 06:33.720
- What do you think?
- Are you out of your mind?

06:34.440 --> 06:35.600
Shouldn't you be
discussing this with your wife?

06:35.680 --> 06:36.520
Why are you discussing it with me?

06:36.600 --> 06:38.520
First, I already
discussed it with my wife.

06:38.600 --> 06:40.840
I just can't hide my excitement.

06:40.920 --> 06:42.400
Secondly, I'm not asking for your opinion.

06:42.480 --> 06:44.400
- I'm just letting you know.
- Hang it up for me.

06:44.480 --> 06:45.600
What?

06:46.880 --> 06:50.120
Sang Yan, why is there
a girl's voice next to you?

06:50.200 --> 06:51.240
It must be your girlfriend, right?

06:51.320 --> 06:53.640
Hi, miss. I'm Qian Fei.

06:53.720 --> 06:55.280
Sang Yan, that's not
very considerate of you.

06:55.360 --> 06:57.360
You said you were
with your roommate, but actually, you--

06:58.800 --> 06:59.920
He hung it up. He's feeling guilty.

07:00.000 --> 07:01.720
You put it on speaker,
but I still couldn't hear clearly.

07:01.800 --> 07:02.640
Whose voice was that?

07:02.720 --> 07:05.920
Someone next to him made a noise.

07:06.000 --> 07:07.040
Anyway, it definitely wasn't Wen Yifan.

07:41.680 --> 07:43.080
Seems like we're almost there.

07:54.880 --> 07:56.280
It's only half past nine.

07:56.360 --> 07:57.360
It's still early.

07:58.040 --> 08:00.360
- Then, let's watch a movie.
- Sure.

08:00.440 --> 08:03.000
I heard that couples kissing
at the top of the Ferris wheel

08:03.080 --> 08:04.560
will stay together forever.

08:04.640 --> 08:05.800
Let's try it.

08:06.320 --> 08:07.800
How about it?

08:08.960 --> 08:10.960
What movie do you want to watch?
Let me check.

08:12.720 --> 08:13.800
Let's go.

08:16.840 --> 08:18.080
Let's ride it again.

08:19.160 --> 08:20.120
What?

08:22.240 --> 08:24.720
The Ferris wheel. Let's ride it again.

08:32.799 --> 08:34.520
Why are you riding again?

08:36.520 --> 08:38.159
We forgot to take a photo.

09:02.560 --> 09:03.400
Wen Shuangjiang.

09:05.720 --> 09:06.680
Weren't we supposed to take a photo?

09:10.240 --> 09:11.080
Right.

09:21.680 --> 09:22.800
What are you taking a picture of?

09:40.280 --> 09:41.200
Why are you laughing?

09:42.880 --> 09:44.000
You're so handsome.

09:46.760 --> 09:49.560
You just look a little bit… arrogant.

09:56.080 --> 09:58.000
How about smiling a little?

09:59.920 --> 10:02.240
When you smile,
your eyes look like crescent moons.

10:02.840 --> 10:03.920
They're curved and cute.

10:04.000 --> 10:06.680
Like crescent moons? I don't have them.

10:06.760 --> 10:09.760
And that mole near your eye

10:10.320 --> 10:11.440
is so noticeable when you smile.

10:12.480 --> 10:14.000
It's like you're smiling with a tear.

10:19.600 --> 10:21.560
It's obviously like a star, okay?

10:21.640 --> 10:23.560
"Smiling with a tear"…
I'm almost crying from laughing.

10:31.960 --> 10:33.160
Get closer.

10:47.720 --> 10:49.320
Can I review the photo?

10:51.320 --> 10:53.160
Let's review it later.

10:59.480 --> 11:00.960
Seems like…

11:02.520 --> 11:03.520
we're almost at the top.

11:05.640 --> 11:08.320
You… heard that, too?

11:13.280 --> 11:14.960
Do you believe in this rumor?

11:16.760 --> 11:18.000
Of course not.

11:18.880 --> 11:20.000
But…

11:21.080 --> 11:22.280
I believe in myself.

11:28.360 --> 11:29.680
This rumor

11:32.120 --> 11:33.440
is made to make you believe it.

12:57.880 --> 12:59.800
Have you reached home?

13:08.000 --> 13:09.280
No need to wait.

13:09.360 --> 13:10.960
Haoan probably won't come.

13:12.320 --> 13:13.800
I wasn't waiting for him.

13:23.120 --> 13:24.280
He,

13:24.360 --> 13:27.280
- did you see Su Haoan today?
- No, I didn't.

13:27.880 --> 13:29.760
When I see him,
I'll tell him to call you back.

13:30.640 --> 13:32.960
No need. I'm leaving now.

13:33.720 --> 13:34.760
Alright, take care.

13:34.840 --> 13:36.800
- Bye.
- Bye.

14:20.440 --> 14:21.640
Did you think I'd try to kiss you again?

14:22.400 --> 14:23.480
Of course not!

14:23.560 --> 14:25.600
I was just thirsty. Get some rest earlier.

14:41.640 --> 14:43.040
QIAO SENT YOU VOICE MESSAGES

14:43.120 --> 14:45.720
QIAO

14:46.920 --> 14:48.680
Have you reached home?

14:50.480 --> 14:52.360
Let me know when you're home.

14:53.960 --> 14:56.000
Are you in a sweet moment?

14:56.080 --> 14:57.640
Then I won't bother you.

14:57.720 --> 14:59.120
I'll go home now.

15:03.000 --> 15:04.520
Yifan, help me.

15:04.600 --> 15:05.920
I'll be late tomorrow.

15:06.000 --> 15:07.960
If the leader asks about me,
just tell him I'm in the bathroom.

15:08.040 --> 15:09.520
Thanks. Love you.

15:10.840 --> 15:11.680
OKAY

15:12.880 --> 15:14.680
Recently, I kept doubting

15:14.760 --> 15:16.480
whether I'm in the real world.

15:17.680 --> 15:19.560
Not only am I loved by Sang Yan,

15:20.120 --> 15:22.320
I also have a group
of really good friends.

15:24.720 --> 15:26.120
Do I really deserve

15:26.200 --> 15:27.960
to be treated like this by everyone?

15:31.240 --> 15:32.080
PRESS AND HOLD TO TALK

15:39.440 --> 15:40.280
Review it before going to sleep.

15:43.120 --> 15:44.160
OKAY

16:33.320 --> 16:36.360
This rumor is made to make you believe it.

17:27.680 --> 17:28.720
Good night.

17:29.760 --> 17:30.640
Good night.

17:30.720 --> 17:32.240
You know what?

17:32.760 --> 17:34.480
The pinyin for good night,

17:36.120 --> 17:39.120
"wan an",

17:40.000 --> 17:41.040
means "I love you".

17:42.960 --> 17:44.560
Do you know that?

17:58.760 --> 18:00.800
IS THIS YOU?
I'M NOT REALLY SURE, SO I'M ASKING

18:12.120 --> 18:13.120
Wen Yifan.

18:16.440 --> 18:17.840
Wen Yifan.

18:27.120 --> 18:28.040
NOW DIALING

18:38.120 --> 18:39.520
It really is you.

18:45.440 --> 18:46.840
I miss you so much.

18:47.960 --> 18:48.800
Yifan.

18:57.600 --> 18:58.560
Hello, Miss Qiao.

18:58.640 --> 19:01.040
- Hello, Mr. Ma.
- You haven't been around for a long time.

19:01.120 --> 19:02.480
Please, come in.

19:02.560 --> 19:04.800
What's that smell?

19:06.320 --> 19:08.800
It's all Woodie Jr.'s fault.

19:08.880 --> 19:11.480
Look, it's peeing all over the house

19:11.560 --> 19:13.120
and making the room

19:13.200 --> 19:14.520
smell terrible.

19:15.200 --> 19:16.040
Where's Grandpa?

19:16.120 --> 19:18.880
You're not allowed to come in! Honestly.

19:19.400 --> 19:21.360
Grandpa, I'm here to see you.

19:24.000 --> 19:26.800
Did someone make you angry?

19:27.400 --> 19:29.600
This Woodie Jr.
is crying and making a fuss.

19:29.680 --> 19:32.200
It's completely different
from my old Woodie.

19:34.120 --> 19:35.160
Grandpa.

19:38.000 --> 19:40.080
If no one can, I'll raise it myself.

19:40.160 --> 19:41.720
Just wait a few days, okay?

19:43.080 --> 19:44.080
Miss Qiao,

19:44.160 --> 19:48.040
would you prefer a drink or tea?

19:48.120 --> 19:49.640
I'm good with anything. Thank you, Mr. Ma.

19:55.840 --> 19:56.960
Grandpa,

19:57.040 --> 19:59.920
I think Woodie Jr. is still a child.

20:00.000 --> 20:01.520
It's peeing everywhere,

20:01.600 --> 20:04.200
maybe because the whole house
smells like the old Woodie.

20:04.280 --> 20:06.080
It wants to change that smell.

20:06.160 --> 20:07.080
Simply put,

20:07.160 --> 20:09.280
it just wants you to care more for it

20:09.360 --> 20:10.680
and love it more.

20:12.200 --> 20:14.880
The old Woodie stayed
with me for 17 years.

20:15.760 --> 20:19.280
Why should it be replaced so quickly?

20:23.360 --> 20:24.800
Grandpa, look,

20:25.520 --> 20:27.640
the old Woodie's toys.
You're still keeping them.

20:28.800 --> 20:30.320
Is it because

20:30.880 --> 20:32.320
you haven't accepted Woodie Jr. yet?

20:35.200 --> 20:38.280
Alright, I'll gradually get used to it.

20:44.680 --> 20:46.880
Do you often think of Grandma?

20:47.440 --> 20:51.040
Haoan and I
already know about your illness.

20:52.000 --> 20:54.640
Then, wouldn't it be better

20:54.720 --> 20:55.640
if Grandma knew, too?

21:02.800 --> 21:04.400
Don't you know

21:04.480 --> 21:07.960
how it feels
when someone suddenly realizes

21:09.080 --> 21:11.120
they're often forgetting things?

21:12.440 --> 21:15.000
I only know
that if I suddenly forget something,

21:15.080 --> 21:16.640
I'll get very anxious.

21:16.720 --> 21:18.360
Right. Now,
I write everything I need to do

21:18.440 --> 21:19.320
on my phone,

21:19.400 --> 21:20.440
so I won't forget.

21:20.520 --> 21:22.680
But the worst part is,

21:22.760 --> 21:25.840
recently, I've even forgotten
how to use my phone.

21:29.440 --> 21:31.040
So, this notebook

21:31.120 --> 21:33.280
is really important to me.

21:40.880 --> 21:42.320
When people get old,

21:42.840 --> 21:45.080
many habits can't be changed.

21:46.920 --> 21:48.160
As for Woodie Jr.,

21:48.240 --> 21:50.560
I'll get used to it slowly.

21:53.840 --> 21:55.680
LAUGHTER LIKES CANDIED HAWS

21:55.760 --> 21:57.000
SHE DOESN'T LIKE SPICY FOOD
SHE LIKES TO TRAVEL

21:58.360 --> 21:59.440
Grandpa,

22:00.080 --> 22:02.560
may I ask

22:02.640 --> 22:04.160
who is "Laughter"?

22:11.440 --> 22:12.880
Look at this.

22:12.960 --> 22:14.040
Who does she look like?

22:16.520 --> 22:18.840
Is this… Grandma?

22:21.680 --> 22:23.720
When she was in a relationship with me,

22:24.480 --> 22:26.360
she laughed so much.

22:27.480 --> 22:30.240
So, I gave her the nickname Laughter.

22:33.240 --> 22:35.840
Later, we often argued.

22:37.320 --> 22:39.160
So, I stopped calling her by her nickname.

22:39.760 --> 22:41.600
But I was afraid I'd forget

22:43.360 --> 22:46.840
about those happy days between me and her.

22:47.360 --> 22:48.680
So,

22:48.760 --> 22:50.400
I had to write everything down quickly.

22:52.440 --> 22:53.640
I really don't want

22:55.480 --> 22:56.600
to forget some things.

23:18.040 --> 23:19.120
Fold the blanket neatly.

23:21.440 --> 23:23.880
- Hello, Qiao.
- Hello, Dian!

23:23.960 --> 23:26.360
You rarely take such a long vacation.

23:26.440 --> 23:28.760
Is there anywhere you want to go?
I'll go with you.

23:28.840 --> 23:30.880
I don't want to go out today.

23:30.960 --> 23:33.280
I want to cook for Sang Yan.

23:33.960 --> 23:36.120
You're actually cooking?

23:36.200 --> 23:37.200
Do you need any help?

23:37.280 --> 23:38.760
I need your help.

23:39.400 --> 23:40.360
Go away.

23:40.440 --> 23:42.920
- No, I want to try it myself.
- Alright.

23:43.000 --> 23:45.520
Then, after you finish,
send me a picture to check.

23:46.920 --> 23:48.120
Okay, bye.

23:52.120 --> 23:55.640
So, this is what a woman in love is like.

23:56.640 --> 24:00.120
UPTOWN FLOWER CITY

24:04.400 --> 24:05.560
IS THIS YOU?
I'M NOT REALLY SURE, SO I'M ASKING

24:05.640 --> 24:07.960
I shouldn't be bothered
by such trivial things.

24:10.240 --> 24:11.120
DELETE

24:17.360 --> 24:18.920
FORTUNE

24:27.640 --> 24:29.760
FORTUNE

24:30.360 --> 24:33.760
Sang Yan should like what I posted.

24:42.520 --> 24:44.160
- Qiao!
- Dian!

24:44.240 --> 24:45.640
I bought you something.

24:47.600 --> 24:49.000
Why did you buy so many things?

24:49.080 --> 24:50.240
I went to the market
to help out this morning

24:50.320 --> 24:51.320
and bought them on the way.

24:51.400 --> 24:53.160
Here's the painting for you. I promised
to give you a painting last time.

24:53.240 --> 24:55.720
- I'll hang it for you.
- You're so nice.

24:55.800 --> 24:56.960
It looks great.

24:57.040 --> 24:58.480
Check if it's straight.

24:58.560 --> 25:00.440
- Move this side down a bit.
- This side?

25:00.520 --> 25:01.440
Is it okay?

25:01.520 --> 25:03.040
Move down a bit more.

25:03.120 --> 25:04.040
- Is it okay?
- Good.

25:06.440 --> 25:09.160
I spent a long time picking this painting.

25:09.240 --> 25:10.920
It symbolizes you and Sang Yan,

25:11.000 --> 25:11.880
hand in hand,

25:11.960 --> 25:13.840
walking through the cold winter together.

25:15.320 --> 25:18.360
I wish you a lifetime of happiness.

25:24.120 --> 25:26.760
Is the size of it too small?

25:26.840 --> 25:29.880
No. Regret is also a kind of beauty.

25:30.840 --> 25:32.640
Well, I'll go then.

25:32.720 --> 25:34.280
Aren't you staying for dinner?

25:34.360 --> 25:36.360
I don't want to interrupt you two.
I'm leaving now.

26:19.280 --> 26:24.640
FORTUNE

27:08.400 --> 27:09.600
You're back.

27:15.040 --> 27:16.160
You've worked hard.

27:16.240 --> 27:18.040
You finally get some rest.
What's keeping you busy?

27:19.640 --> 27:21.280
I made you a nice meal.

27:21.880 --> 27:23.120
It's to return your favor.

27:24.520 --> 27:25.920
You made it?

27:26.520 --> 27:27.560
You made it yourself?

27:30.280 --> 27:31.240
It's not bought?

27:39.200 --> 27:40.360
Why…

27:41.080 --> 27:42.760
Make it like a candlelight… dinner.

27:44.440 --> 27:45.280
A simple version.

27:47.040 --> 27:49.040
I'm starting to eat.

28:01.440 --> 28:03.120
You're eating so casually?

28:04.640 --> 28:05.680
Aren't you going to comment?

28:06.280 --> 28:07.120
What else would you expect?

28:07.200 --> 28:08.720
Do you want me to say it's incredible

28:08.800 --> 28:10.880
or that it's unbelievably delicious?

28:12.880 --> 28:14.120
What if I poisoned it?

28:25.200 --> 28:26.840
Then you should eat it, too.

28:26.920 --> 28:28.160
Let's go together later.

28:30.000 --> 28:31.000
Don't you know that the person who cooks

28:31.080 --> 28:32.200
usually doesn't have an appetite to eat?

28:32.280 --> 28:34.600
But when I cook,
I usually have a good appetite.

28:36.960 --> 28:39.320
- What's this?
- Tofu soup.

28:41.560 --> 28:42.400
Here.

28:47.520 --> 28:48.760
Let me taste it.

28:53.560 --> 28:54.680
There's tofu in it.

28:57.960 --> 29:00.160
Actually, I've always wanted to tell you.

29:00.880 --> 29:02.480
These little lights…

29:03.280 --> 29:04.680
don't really do anything.

29:05.600 --> 29:07.480
Because when we sleepwalk,

29:07.560 --> 29:09.080
we don't really react to light.

29:10.680 --> 29:12.280
We just follow
the usual path during the day

29:12.360 --> 29:13.640
and go with some sensations.

29:17.440 --> 29:19.040
But I'm still really touched.

29:22.320 --> 29:23.280
I'll take them down later.

29:30.080 --> 29:32.520
How come I never noticed
you're so dramatic before?

29:33.680 --> 29:35.040
Maybe you didn't get enough to eat.

29:38.760 --> 29:40.640
But since being with you,

29:40.720 --> 29:42.400
my sleepwalking has decreased a lot.

29:43.840 --> 29:45.640
It feels like pressure
doesn't matter anymore.

29:46.240 --> 29:48.440
These words make me pretty happy.

29:48.520 --> 29:49.960
At least I'm more useful
than the little lights.

29:53.400 --> 29:54.840
What I mean is…

30:01.680 --> 30:03.640
No matter what, you'll always catch me.

30:14.400 --> 30:15.760
I'm okay.

30:16.640 --> 30:17.680
Eat up.

30:20.920 --> 30:21.760
Wen Yifan.

30:26.560 --> 30:27.800
No matter what,

30:30.640 --> 30:31.840
I will always catch you.

30:43.120 --> 30:44.200
Eat up.

30:45.320 --> 30:47.320
From now on, you have
to speak up about anything.

30:48.440 --> 30:50.000
Or else, I'll just keep
drawing butterflies for you.

30:52.400 --> 30:53.560
Are you tired today?

30:54.160 --> 30:55.360
No.

30:55.440 --> 30:57.800
Then later, how about watching a movie?

30:58.640 --> 31:00.600
I heard there's
a good thriller movie recently.

31:05.240 --> 31:06.400
Aren't you tired?

31:06.920 --> 31:08.800
No. I slept all day.

31:10.120 --> 31:11.120
Let's watch it later.

31:14.400 --> 31:15.760
Wen Shuangjiang,

31:17.560 --> 31:19.960
was your main goal
just to watch the movie,

31:21.800 --> 31:23.040
or was it to be with me?

31:25.440 --> 31:26.480
You.

31:27.000 --> 31:28.680
I want to watch a movie with you.

31:31.680 --> 31:33.000
Finish the dishes.

31:42.560 --> 31:46.080
- It's movie time!
- Okay.

31:48.240 --> 31:49.160
It's not a horror movie, right?

31:49.240 --> 31:50.960
Do you want to watch a horror movie?

31:51.520 --> 31:52.680
I'll change it for you. Here.

31:52.760 --> 31:54.480
Though it's a pity, but it's fine.

31:54.560 --> 31:55.600
Maybe next time.

31:55.680 --> 31:56.560
- Let's change it.
- No need.

32:23.800 --> 32:24.880
I can't believe this.

32:24.960 --> 32:27.360
Your relatives from your dad's side
are so shameless.

32:27.440 --> 32:29.280
They've been at our house
for a week already.

32:29.360 --> 32:31.000
Do they want to live here long-term?

32:32.640 --> 32:34.880
No matter what,
you're closer to them, right?

32:34.960 --> 32:37.080
Can you take them away soon?

32:42.160 --> 32:45.800
Also, your aunt
keeps asking Mom for money.

32:47.160 --> 32:48.120
What does it have to do with us

32:48.200 --> 32:49.960
that her son is buying
a house to get married?

32:57.480 --> 32:59.000
If you want to watch a movie with me,

32:59.080 --> 33:00.400
can you focus for a moment?

33:01.960 --> 33:03.200
Got it.

33:10.080 --> 33:11.320
I'll throw my phone aside.

33:17.360 --> 33:19.200
So, they've all come to Nanwu.

33:20.000 --> 33:21.080
Why?

33:21.920 --> 33:24.000
Why the face all of a sudden?

33:26.760 --> 33:28.800
Nothing. Focus on the movie.

33:32.000 --> 33:33.880
Then, want some fruit?

33:33.960 --> 33:34.920
I'll go get it.

33:53.440 --> 33:56.080
ZHENG KEJIA: MOM ASKS
WILL YOU COME HOME FOR NEW YEAR HOLIDAY?

34:00.360 --> 34:01.680
When did you get your holiday?

34:02.960 --> 34:03.920
Your New Year holiday.

34:07.400 --> 34:09.239
I've been off since the little New Year.

34:09.960 --> 34:13.159
Ms. Qian specifically told me
I can't work overtime this time.

34:17.320 --> 34:18.199
Are you going home?

34:19.320 --> 34:20.239
No.

34:23.199 --> 34:24.760
Let me calculate…

34:27.120 --> 34:27.960
What are you calculating?

34:30.080 --> 34:31.719
Calculating when
I should come back to see you.

34:36.800 --> 34:38.400
Why are you back?

34:38.480 --> 34:41.320
Didn't you say
that you won't be back until the 8th day?

34:41.400 --> 34:43.000
There are too many relatives at home.

34:43.080 --> 34:44.320
I don't have a place to stay.

34:49.520 --> 34:51.800
Last year, you suddenly
came back on New Year's Eve.

34:52.480 --> 34:54.600
Was it because you don't
like spending New Year's at home,

34:55.480 --> 34:56.600
or…

34:58.080 --> 34:59.280
Or what?

34:59.360 --> 35:00.720
Or did I come back for you specifically?

35:03.640 --> 35:04.680
Did you?

35:18.480 --> 35:19.440
Sang Yan,

35:21.400 --> 35:22.680
don't you want to know

35:22.760 --> 35:24.840
why I didn't go back to celebrate
the New Year with my mom?

35:26.680 --> 35:27.920
I believe you will tell me

35:28.000 --> 35:29.160
when you're ready.

35:31.000 --> 35:32.280
Just now,

35:32.840 --> 35:35.080
Zheng Kejia sent me some messages.

35:36.880 --> 35:39.520
She said my mom asked if
I'm going home for the New Year.

35:41.080 --> 35:42.000
But my relationship
with my stepfather's side

35:42.080 --> 35:43.560
isn't very good.

35:52.400 --> 35:55.760
Soon after my dad passed away,

35:57.080 --> 35:58.680
my mom remarried.

36:03.040 --> 36:04.560
This is Uncle Zheng.

36:04.640 --> 36:08.000
He's been helping since your dad got sick.

36:08.600 --> 36:10.240
Why are you silent? Greet him.

36:10.320 --> 36:12.120
You're so impolite!

36:18.200 --> 36:19.160
What is

36:20.000 --> 36:21.920
your plan for Yifan?

36:26.440 --> 36:27.400
What's wrong?

36:30.320 --> 36:31.160
Nothing.

36:34.320 --> 36:35.760
I suddenly feel…

36:38.000 --> 36:39.320
I'm glad I skipped class that day.

36:48.200 --> 36:49.480
So, what happened later?

36:49.560 --> 36:52.440
Why didn't you stay with your mom
and stepdad?

36:54.520 --> 36:56.120
We didn't get along.

36:59.240 --> 37:01.160
Not long after,
I went to my grandma's place.

37:01.240 --> 37:03.440
Yifan, I really miss you.

37:04.080 --> 37:05.560
She cared so much about my dad,

37:06.240 --> 37:07.720
so she cared for me, too.

37:12.240 --> 37:13.840
Being cared for

37:18.320 --> 37:19.920
is ultimately happy, right?

37:22.720 --> 37:24.400
Even when life is tough.

37:31.520 --> 37:33.200
I was sent to my uncle's house

37:35.640 --> 37:37.840
when Grandma got sick.

37:39.800 --> 37:41.440
I rarely hear you talk about these things.

37:43.440 --> 37:44.680
What about your stepsister?

37:45.800 --> 37:47.800
During the last dinner gathering,

37:48.560 --> 37:50.400
she acted like
she was really close to you.

37:53.440 --> 37:55.160
That's just her personality.

37:55.880 --> 37:57.560
She's been pampered

37:58.080 --> 38:00.160
since she was little.

38:01.200 --> 38:02.920
She always had the best of everything.

38:04.040 --> 38:05.400
She never settled for less.

38:08.680 --> 38:11.360
Even if there's a problem or a difficulty,

38:12.200 --> 38:13.960
she always gets others to solve it.

38:16.680 --> 38:18.760
And I'm a few years older than her,

38:18.840 --> 38:20.760
so it's only right to tolerate her.

38:24.960 --> 38:26.360
Tolerate her?

38:27.360 --> 38:28.840
Where did that rule come from?

38:34.920 --> 38:37.240
You never tolerate your younger sister.

39:02.000 --> 39:03.560
Can you eat properly?

39:04.800 --> 39:06.560
Your bones are hurting me.

39:07.480 --> 39:08.880
When will you gain some weight?

39:08.960 --> 39:11.080
My friends say I've gained weight.

39:11.640 --> 39:13.320
What nonsense.

39:14.280 --> 39:15.720
Are they purposely trying to annoy me?

39:17.200 --> 39:19.640
Is something wrong with you?

39:19.720 --> 39:22.320
You want me to gain weight.
If I get fat, you'll pick on others.

39:24.320 --> 39:25.840
Then you can attack me personally.

39:38.320 --> 39:39.160
Wen Shuangjiang.

39:42.200 --> 39:44.360
Don't project
your stepsister's harsh words

39:45.120 --> 39:48.280
and those nonsensical standards onto me.

39:48.360 --> 39:49.200
Do you understand?

39:50.960 --> 39:53.320
Do you think everything in this house
was bought randomly?

39:54.480 --> 39:55.480
Every item,

39:56.280 --> 39:57.360
each one,

39:58.320 --> 39:59.360
was chosen for you.

40:01.200 --> 40:02.240
Also,

40:03.480 --> 40:05.600
you said your stepsister
has been pampered?

40:06.240 --> 40:08.440
Just because of your taste
in choosing a partner,

40:10.880 --> 40:12.920
you deserve the best of everything.

40:13.000 --> 40:14.080
Got it?

41:01.920 --> 41:06.440
REVIEW IT BEFORE GOING TO SLEEP

42:00.480 --> 42:02.000
- How many people are in your group?
- Two.

42:03.400 --> 42:04.520
Thank you.

45:14.520 --> 45:15.360
HUGE THANKS TO EVERYONE INVOLVED
AND TO ALL THE FANS OF THE FIRST FROST!

45:15.440 --> 45:16.280
TREAT YOURSELF WELL
AND THE WORLD WILL HOLD MORE LOVE FOR YOU!
